  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink48-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">parattaiyarmāṭṭu oḻukāniṉṟu taṉ maṉaikkaṭ ceṉṟa talaimakaṟkut talaimakaḷ
          colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink48">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> valaival pāṇmakaṉ vāleyiṟṟu maṭamakaḷ </l>
          <l> varāal corinta vaṭṭiyuṇ maṉaiyōḷ</l>
          <l> yāṇṭukaḻi veṇṇe ṉiṟaikku mūra</l>
          <l> vēṇṭēm perumaniṉ parattai</l>
          <l> yāṇṭuccey kuṟiyō ṭīṇṭunī varalē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> O man from a village! </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> Where a wife [takes] year-old, white paddy </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> and fills a basket [already] emptied of Varāal fish </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> by the bard's innocent daughter– </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> he so dextrous with nets,</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> she with the pure-white teeth. </l>
          <l> O big-man! We don't want you to come here</l>
          <l> with marks made there by your other woman.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
